summary: Both REQ-1 and REQ-2 appear to be implemented. The actor-not-available alert has been removed and replaced with a graceful loading state in Services.tsx, and a Contact Number field has been added to the booking form, backend WorkOrder type, and admin WorkOrders view. All major acceptance criteria are covered.

hallucinated_features.description: A migration module (backend/migration.mo) was added to handle data migration for existing WorkOrder records when the new customerContactNumber field is introduced.
hallucinated_features.reason: The build request does not mention adding a migration module or handling existing data migration. This is an extra implementation not requested in any requirement.
